## Limitations
The information gathered is based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of the refugee experience. The data is also limited to the sources accessed, which may not represent the full spectrum of reasons why refugees flee. Additionally, the rapidly changing geopolitical landscape can alter the dynamics of refugee movements, making some information outdated quickly.